title: The Big Hit-Lou Diamond Phillips, Mark Wahlberg
description:
Movie Description
Mel (Mark Wahlberg) is a neurotic, overworked hit man working for two crime bosses--Cisco (Lou Diamond Phillips) and Paris (Avery Brooks). He has a demanding fiance (Christina Applegate) with parents he&#039;s trying to impress and a gold-digging mistress (Lela Rochon) to occupy his scarce free time. Cisco proposes that stressed-out Mel kidnap Keiko (China Chow), the young daughter of Jiro Nishi, a wealthy Japanese industrialist. Mel captures her, but unfortunately Cisco is unaware that she is the goddaughter of Paris, who promptly puts a separate crew out to find and destroy Keiko&#039;s captors---and Paris is unaware that Mel is the man they are looking for. This unique and violent blend of action and comedy was executive produced by John Woo

Credits 
Cast: Christina Applegate, Lou Diamond Phillips, Mark Wahlberg 
Director: Che-Kirk Wong 
Producer: Warren Zide, Wesley Snipes
